tters/?source=hp-tile" class="inline-flex gap-1 font-bold outline-none ring-blue-600 ring-offset-2 hover:drop-shadow-md focus:ring-2 bg-white text-black hover:border-gray-800 hover:bg-gray-50 focus:bg-gray-50 text-sm rounded-lg py-2 px-6"><span>Subscribe to our newsletters</span></a></div><section class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-4 sm:gap-6 sm:grid-cols-4 mb-4" data-testid="grid"><div class="group relative flex overflow-hidden col-span-2 row-span-4 border-t pt-4" data-testid="ImmutableGridSlot"><a href="https://theconversation.com/what-students-protesting-israels-gaza-siege-want-and-how-their-demands-on-divestment-fit-into-the-bds-movement-228772" class="group relative flex min-h-96 w-full flex-col justify-end sm:min-h-80 lg:min-h-96 xl:min-h-120"><div class="absolute inset-0 hidden md:block"><img alt="Woman in sunglasses waves a Palestinian red, green, white and black flag surrounded by people wearing keffiyah." loading="lazy" decoding="async" data-nimg="fill" class="object-cover" style="position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;color:transparent;background-size:cover;background-position:50% 50%;background-repeat:no-repeat;background-image:url(&quot;data:image/svg+xml;charset=utf-8,%3Csvg xmlns=&#x27;http%3A//www.w3.org/2000/svg&#x27;%3E%3Cimage style=&#x27;filter:blur(20px)&#x27; preserveAspectRatio=&#x27;none&#x27; x=&#x27;0&#x27; y=&#x27;0&#x27; height=&#x27;100%25&#x27; width=&#x27;100%25&#x27; href=&#x27;data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAPAAAC1PTv///yH5BAAAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==&#x27;/%3E%3C/svg%3E&quot;)" sizes="(min-width: 1466px) 678px, (min-width: 1024px) 486px, (min-width: 640px) 50vw, 100vw" srcSet="https://images.theconversation.com/files/591524/original/file-20240501-18-k7ugx1.jpg?q=30&amp;usm=12&amp;cs=strip&amp;w=384&amp;auto=format&amp;rect=83%2C70%2C4184%2C2463&amp;fit=crop 384w, https://images.theconversation.com/files/591524/original/file-20240501-18-k7ugx1.jpg?q=30&amp;usm=12&amp;cs=strip&amp;w=640&amp;auto=format&